{"tid":824700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 【蝗蟲話之你】沙田城門河滿目瘡痍　大媽舞照跳","createTime":"2018-09-17T07:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T10:15:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed218867d730ea5a2df16aeb75ec8bdcbb106cf","tid":824700,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"城門河兩岸亦有大量共享單車混雜樹枝雜物，被吹成一團，如同共享單車墳場。有清潔工人指，她連日常工作的工具都被吹走，面對一片混亂的現場，根本不知從何開始清理。但即使環境再亂，有一件事仍是雷打不動，就是高聲播放音樂、在廣場跳舞的一眾大媽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/152803_188877a6eabe075ad414cdeb7d393b3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F152803_188877a6eabe075ad414cdeb7d393b3e.png&h=f5c2b7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/236410/颱風山竹-沙田城門河滿目瘡痍-神秘石躉吹上路-大媽舞照跳\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F236410%2F%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%9F%8E%E9%96%80%E6%B2%B3%E6%BB%BF%E7%9B%AE%E7%98%A1%E7%97%8D-%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%9F%B3%E8%BA%89%E5%90%B9%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E8%88%9E%E7%85%A7%E8%B7%B3&d=XW%2Bx1RxpNmsuaiIKIWoQWUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c7af4e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/236410/颱風山竹-沙田城門河滿目瘡痍-神秘石躉吹上路-大媽舞照跳</a>"},{"pid":"b0a858461ee6bd8a3c93d19fe7fea925b45586f6","tid":824700,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fed6b207fc49544d21335a44daca2e5e828bd0","tid":824700,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"none care u，我理你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93ab596ea3e7c40c9ca21935ca61c958582f47f","tid":824700,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1